maxima and minimum points and
inflection points, and all the

00:00:09.410 --> 00:00:12.490
like that you normally see in
your first semester of

00:00:12.490 --> 00:00:13.320
a calculus course.

00:00:13.320 --> 00:00:16.170
So, I thought I would
start doing them.

00:00:16.170 --> 00:00:19.140
But before we kind of go into
the actual problems that you

00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:20.980
